{"tid":103234,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"扶桑國到底在哪裏？並不是日本，而是一個美洲國家","createTime":"2017-02-01T07:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T09:10:17.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f90f0312dfa234bd16b547d074946d4b8a4255d9","tid":103234,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:46:09.000Z","msg":"扶桑是中國古代所流傳的一種神樹，而我國古代歷史上也記載了一個名叫「扶桑國」的國家。說起扶桑國，人們更是第一反應就會想起日本。<br />\n<br />\n認為日本是扶桑國的人是這麼覺得的，因為在我國歷史上，扶桑樹是和太陽有關的神樹。而根據我國的《海外東經》的記載「湯谷上有扶桑。十日所浴，在黑齒北，居水中。」<br />\n在這本書中，記載了扶桑樹所在的地理位置，說是在黑齒國的北邊。而這個所謂的黑齒國就有趣了，因為在歷史上，真的有這麼一個叫黑齒國的地方。<br />\n<br />\nADVERTISEMENT<br />\n根據明朝《日本考》所記載，到明朝時期的時候，日本貴族不知道為什麼，流行把牙齒染成黑齒。所以，根據他的記載和其他的一些記載，可以考據出，黑齒國就存在在日本。也就是說，扶桑在黑齒國的北邊，而黑齒國又在日本島上，所以，扶桑國就是日本。<br />\n<br />\n當然，這是古代很多人的想法。<br />\n但是，到了近代以來，人們發現，扶桑國或許根本就不是日本，而是一個美洲國家。<br />\n<br />\n這是一個法國人所提出的觀點。他認為，扶桑國不是日本，而是墨西哥。他更在1761年的時候，說：「根據中國史書，在公元5世紀的時候，中國的僧人已經到達了扶桑，而扶桑就是墨西哥。」<br />\nADVERTISEMENT<br />\n他的這個說法和觀點獲得了很多人的同意，他們認為按照《梁書、扶桑傳》所記載，真正的扶桑是墨西哥，而不是日本。<br />\n<br />\n因為，他們說，這扶桑樹，其實就是古代墨西哥人的「龍舌蘭」。並且這個到達扶桑國的僧人&mdash;&mdash;慧深，他從中國出發，先向東北航行，最後到達了扶桑國，而他是利用季候風和海洋風到達目的地。<br />\n而很有可能，他到的這個扶桑國就是現在的墨西哥。除了扶桑樹類似之外，墨西哥北部的巨大的野牛也和《梁書》所記載的一樣。<br />\n<br />\nADVERTISEMENT<br />\n所以，這個扶桑國，很可能就是墨西哥，而不是日本。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/894ravq.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhistory%2F894ravq.html&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=f8df9f06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/894ravq.html</a>"},{"pid":"d3a8b2426807a11fd41fdeda72008d167d1c3f3d","tid":103234,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307e972701edaef71a278e1c128cdcdf06e62249","tid":103234,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:15:33.000Z","msg":"咪又打飛機話中國去過美洲啦"},{"pid":"dad9ea1c592e68c692d6cab19ef6e31f0750d345","tid":103234,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:21:05.000Z","msg":"明明兩三段就講完<br />\n係都要拖長係咁跨張其詞講廢話"},{"pid":"08e40e89457acb20896ba80d10b91619af8d3f59","tid":103234,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:23:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明兩三段就講完<br />\n係都要拖長係咁跨張其詞講廢話</blockquote><br />\n所以，這個扶桑國，很可能就是墨西哥，而不是日本。<br />\n<br />\n直SKIP到最尾一句"},{"pid":"4e5839acb0a6d65e2db4c2a96d33ad30ea08ae9b","tid":103234,"uid":3068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:23:16.000Z","msg":"飛機文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a68e44227fd5fe73f4ca3d52ddb572915f34b979","tid":103234,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:24:32.000Z","msg":"布笑，露黑齒"},{"pid":"837420d21f8c442092c3320f631ab0d79bbffac1","tid":103234,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T04:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d38865a2249338ff62e84168f8d3f0905ed37d","tid":103234,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T04:43:34.000Z","msg":"用季候風坐船去墨西哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f807bb752e634ca5068734a361fb577d6ae74d53","tid":103234,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:09:12.000Z","msg":"支那人搵到新大陸"},{"pid":"ca973b1c58f29a1d9b4d2b84453fc7f905184808","tid":103234,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T03:52:47.000Z","msg":"這是一個法國人所提出的觀點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係我講嫁 人地都係咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> is<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n飛機文"},{"pid":"ea677887791b5b7a67456921096fa2f16ba614f4","tid":103234,"uid":47451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T04:02:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>布笑，露黑齒</blockquote><br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee7441d3a34176b609cc0dd3485a518f8bbda23","tid":103234,"uid":19664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T09:02:48.000Z","msg":"Logic failed <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe824cc1f75aac9f9da202ef0e59c08518e9200","tid":103234,"uid":63618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T09:10:17.000Z","msg":"中國向東北，淨係用季候風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用呢個方法依家既人去唔去到墨西哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}